column3: Honey Final Estimates 1998-2002: Released April 29, 2004, by the National Agricultural Statistics Service (NASS), Agricultural Statistics Board, U.S. Department of Agriculture.
Honey:  Number of Colonies, Yield, Production, Stocks, Price,
and Value by State and United States,  1998 1/

1/  For producers with 5 or more colonies.  2/  Stocks held by producers.   3/  CT, DE, MA, NH, RI, and SC not published separately to avoid disclosing data for individual operations.  4/  U.S. price weighted by survey expanded sales.  Total may not add due to rounding.
